{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05748/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05748"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:57:48"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["exterior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A group of people arrive at a townhome, greeting a man and a woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05748","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05748"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1/3d6e4cf8-44b7-4a4e-a486-3c5cd035f347","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T15:00:36.567Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In a compilation of screen tests, PTA explains that Lesley Manville, the actress who plays Cyril, “has a face that is a stop and a half brighter than everybody else, she has luminescent skin, as they say” (“<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW240224385 BCX0\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LY2cCWBS05c\"><u>‘Phantom Thread’ Camera Tests, Narrated by Paul Thomas Anderson</u></a>”). It is no surprise then that she is tasked with welcoming Princess Mona Braganza and her posse to the House of Woodcock alongside Reynolds. In this shot, she is standing atop the steps that lead to the house’s front door: she is “a stop and a half” above as she greets the royal.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05748/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1479.9964162844037,426.86138188073403,210.09891055045887,413.8180905963303"}}}]}]}]}